  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to compare short term (3 week) with long term (6 months) treatment
      with seton prior to LIFT surgery. The main end-points are recurrence rates and complication
      rates after surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
